# NovaSpend UI/UX

## Design ratio: 90% minimal / 10% glass

- **Default:** flat surfaces, generous whitespace, no decorative clutter.
- **Glass (sparingly):** use `GlassSurface` only for nav bars, bottom sheets, floating panels, or one hero element per screen — never on every card.
- Glass = subtle blur + low-opacity fill + thin border. No heavy gradients or neon.

## Native platform feel

- Prefer platform-adaptive widgets: `AdaptiveScaffold`, Material on Android, Cupertino on iOS where it matters (navigation, dialogs, switches).
- Respect platform safe areas and system fonts (SF Pro on iOS, Roboto on Android via theme).
- Use `Theme.of(context).platform` or `defaultTargetPlatform` — do not force iOS chrome on Android or vice versa.

## Tokens (use these, do not magic-number in widgets)

| Token | Location | Values |
|-------|----------|--------|
| Accent | `AppColors.accent` | Single green `#10B981` — only accent hue in the app |
| Radius | `AppRadius` | `md` 16, `lg` 20, `xl` 24 |
| Spacing | `AppSpacing` | `xs` 4 … `xxl` 48 — charts/lists need `lg`+ padding |
| Motion | `AppMotion` | 200–350 ms, `Curves.easeOutCubic` |

Import from `lib/core/theme/`.

## Layout patterns

### Large balance at top

- Primary screens (home, analytics) lead with `BalanceHeader`: large amount (`displayLarge` / 36–48 sp), muted label above, accent only on positive/trend indicators.
- Balance sits in top third; actions below, not competing with the number.

### Clean cards

- Use `AppCard` for list items and grouped content: white/dark surface, `AppRadius.lg`, soft shadow or 1 px border — no glass on standard cards.
- One concept per card; 16 px internal padding minimum.

### Charts

- Simple line/bar only; muted grid lines; accent color for primary series, grey for secondary.
- Minimum 24 px padding around chart; no 3D, no legend boxes unless necessary.
- Prefer `fl_chart` (when added) with minimal axis labels.

## Animations

- Page transitions: 300 ms ease-out.
- List insert/remove: `AnimatedList` or implicit `AnimatedSwitcher` (~250 ms).
- Balance/count updates: short scale or fade — never bounce or elastic on money values.
- Respect `MediaQuery.disableAnimations` / reduced motion.

## Color rules

- **One accent** (`AppColors.accent`) for CTAs, active nav, positive trends, chart primary series.
- Neutrals for text (`primary`, `secondary`, `tertiary` from theme).
- Semantic colors (error red, warning amber) only for status — not decoration.

## Do / Don't

| Do | Don't |
|----|-------|
| Whitespace between sections (`AppSpacing.lg`+) | Dense stacked cards |
| `context.l10n` for all copy | Hardcoded labels |
| Shared widgets in `core/widgets/` | Duplicate card styles per feature |
| Glass on ≤1 surface per screen | Full glassmorphism theme |
| Theme tokens | Inline `Color(0xFF…)` in features |

## File placement

- Design tokens: `lib/core/theme/`
- Reusable UI: `lib/core/widgets/` (`AppCard`, `GlassSurface`, `BalanceHeader`, `AdaptiveScaffold`)
- Feature-specific layouts: `features/<feature>/presentation/widgets/`
